subject: Taekwondo
lead_paragraph: Iran withdrew from a tae kwon do final against Israel at the inaugural Youth Olympics in Singapore on Sunday, the same day Iran’s girls soccer team beat Papua New Guinea, 1-0, after reaching a compromise on Islamic head scarves.
